{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the production and sale of pointed knives",
        "additional_details": "So many innocent life lost because of knife crime. We believe there is no need for a knife to have a pointed end. Knives do so much harm.\r\n \r\nEven in the kitchen the pointed end of the knife is rarely used. But most kitchen knives have a pointed end.\r\n \r\nSo many innocent life lost due to penetrating injury by the pointed end of a knife, which can easily cause potentially fatal injuries to arteries and organs.\r\n \r\nThat's why I think there is no need for pointed knives.\r\n",
        "background": "We want the Government to make it illegal to produce or sell pointed knives, to help prevent knife crime.",
